		    <div class="span2">
		      <%=image_tag "icons/star2.png", title: "Advanced Beginner"%>
		    </div>
		    <div class="span10" style="padding-top:;">
		      <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Advanced Beginner</h3>
		      <p>
		        It's probably best to start by working through the curriculum. Much of
		        it may be familiar, but most people report filling in large gaps they
		        didn't even know they had. If you feel ready (and even if you don't), 
		        it's time to consider getting involved with the project.
		      </p>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		</div>

